OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778163069
OL,3,CWetherspoons boss attacks Ryanair's
OL,4,Ccall to limit airport drinking
OL,6,FJD Wetherspoons boss Sir Tim Martin
OL,7,Fhas criticised Ryanair's proposed
OL,8,Fcrackdown on early morning pints at
OL,9,Fairports, calling it a "Big Brother"
OL,10,Fapproach.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, Ryanair's CEO Michael
OL,13,FO'Leary called for airports to ban the
OL,14,Fearly-morning pint and introduce a two-
OL,15,Fdrink limit to tackle bad behaviour on
OL,16,Fflights.
OL,18,FBut in an interview with The Times
OL,19,Fpublished on Thursday, Sir Tim said
OL,20,Fany limit would be difficult to manage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
