OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778163069
OL,3,CWetherspoons boss attacks Ryanair's
OL,4,Ccall to limit airport drinking
OL,6,F"It is in everyone's interests to have
OL,7,Fgood behaviour at airports and on
OL,8,Fflights," he said.
OL,10,F"A two-drink limit would be
OL,11,Fextraordinarily difficult to
OL,12,Fimplement, short of breathalysing
OL,13,Fpassengers, and would, in our opinion,
OL,14,Fbe an overreaction, especially since
OL,15,Fmany of the problems stem from
OL,16,Fincoming flights."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
