OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778163069
OL,3,CWetherspoons boss attacks Ryanair's
OL,4,Ccall to limit airport drinking
OL,6,FWetherspoons said in a statement that
OL,7,Fimposing drink limits at airports
OL,8,Fcould push passengers towards "off-
OL,9,Ftrade sales", with people possibly
OL,10,Fbuying alcohol from supermarkets or
OL,11,Foff-licences before arriving.
OL,13,FThe pub chain said its airport venues
OL,14,Fwere "highly supervised" environments
OL,15,Fwith strict policies to prevent
OL,16,Fexcessive drinking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
