OL,3,CWetherspoons boss attacks Ryanair's
OL,4,Ccall to limit airport drinking
OL,6,FWetherspoons also said it had "never
OL,7,Fbeen suggested" that its customers
OL,8,Fwere responsible for disruption on
OL,9,Fflights, and claimed most of its sales
OL,10,Fwere not alcohol-related.
OL,12,FO'Leary had earlier said that Ryanair
OL,13,Fwas diverting almost one flight a day
OL,14,Fon average because of disruptive
OL,15,Fpassenger behaviour, partly due to
OL,16,Falcohol.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
